1
00:00:00,250 --> 00:00:02,210
I'm going to turn you into a prince.

2
00:00:10,890 --> 00:00:13,810
This is the story of how I, the School Festival Prince,

3
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:16,640
and that guy spent the days
leading up to our anniversary.

4
00:00:23,650 --> 00:00:24,360
By the way...

5
00:00:24,360 --> 00:00:27,070
I haven't been able to see Makoto
at all lately!

6
00:00:27,070 --> 00:00:29,820
My Makoto energy is running dangerously low!

7
00:00:29,820 --> 00:00:33,070
Well, he is a popular
rising model now.

8
00:00:35,200 --> 00:00:36,700
(Must-Have Mix-and-Match Items)

9
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:38,370
Whoa!

10
00:00:38,370 --> 00:00:39,710
Amazing.

11
00:00:39,710 --> 00:00:40,540
Right?

12
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:43,250
Even though I was the one who gave him that makeover...

13
00:00:44,090 --> 00:00:45,090
Anyway!

14
00:00:45,090 --> 00:00:47,590
Our anniversary is coming up.
I wonder if he's free?

15
00:00:47,590 --> 00:00:49,100
What are you waiting for?

16
00:00:49,510 --> 00:00:51,340
Just text him already!

17
00:00:51,340 --> 00:00:52,390
Hurry up!

18
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:53,510
Right now?

19
00:00:53,510 --> 00:00:54,140
Yes!

20
00:00:55,180 --> 00:00:56,180
Uh...

21
00:00:57,220 --> 00:00:58,520
Hmm...

22
00:01:01,190 --> 00:01:02,400
Hmm...

23
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:03,400
Oh! Nice!

24
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:04,810
Looking sharp!

25
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,110
Great!

26
00:01:06,110 --> 00:01:06,570
Perfect! Look over here.

27
00:01:06,570 --> 00:01:08,030
You look so mature!

28
00:01:08,030 --> 00:01:09,150
That's absolutely gorgeous!

29
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:10,110
Incredible!

30
00:01:10,110 --> 00:01:11,860
And that's a wrap!
Great job, everyone!

31
00:01:11,860 --> 00:01:13,240
- Thank you, everyone!
- Thank you!

32
00:01:13,240 --> 00:01:14,280
Thank you.

33
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:15,030
Good work.

34
00:01:15,030 --> 00:01:15,990
Good work.

35
00:01:15,990 --> 00:01:17,240
Great job today, Makoto.

36
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:18,580
Thank you,
Shiono-san.

37
00:01:18,660 --> 00:01:19,660
Makoto.

38
00:01:19,660 --> 00:01:21,460
Now that the shoot is over,

39
00:01:21,460 --> 00:01:23,000
do you have a moment to talk?

40
00:01:24,710 --> 00:01:26,500
(Makoto, great job today.
Can we meet up in the next couple of days?)

41
00:01:26,500 --> 00:01:27,500
Sure.

42
00:01:27,500 --> 00:01:29,380
Can I reply to a message first?

43
00:01:29,800 --> 00:01:30,800
Of course.

44
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:42,100
Sorry, I'm still working.

45
00:01:42,100 --> 00:01:45,110
I'll share my schedule with you later.

46
00:01:46,940 --> 00:01:50,400
It's always "later" with him lately!

47
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:53,700
You're keeping me waiting too long,
my Prince Charming.

48
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,790
Delivery's here!

49
00:01:59,790 --> 00:02:00,870
Up we go.

50
00:02:00,870 --> 00:02:02,210
I'm so hungry!

51
00:02:02,210 --> 00:02:03,540
Coming!

52
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:05,330
Hey.

53
00:02:05,790 --> 00:02:08,040
Wait, Makoto?!
